Simulates sun light scattering through the atmosphere.
Scale the number of entities in each unit in battle.
Control the amount of blur distant objects receive beyond the focus point of the camera.
The level of detail used by the sky in battle and campaign.
The level of detail used by lighting in battle and campaign.
Select how long bodies of defeated warriors in battle should remain on the field, before they are removed. Selecting never will keep those bodies on the field until the battle ends.
